    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >悄无声息地接近，不要让他们听到你的声音...</h2><br><strong>你准备好进入这个黑暗世界了吗？</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049150/extras/695007db2e60826c26038f6bb018c6f7.poster.avif?t=1749902158\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049150/extras/695007db2e60826c26038f6bb018c6f7.webm?t=1749902158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049150/extras/695007db2e60826c26038f6bb018c6f7.mp4?t=1749902158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>通过你的选择，你将决定这次旅程的目的。你是要醒来发现真相，还是要继续生活在谎言中？<br>加入亚伦的超现实旅程，找到答案。<i>有时在天空下，有时在墙壁的阴影中。</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049150/extras/86c99df4504e4a286552c3f1f4a664de.poster.avif?t=1749902158\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049150/extras/86c99df4504e4a286552c3f1f4a664de.webm?t=1749902158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049150/extras/86c99df4504e4a286552c3f1f4a664de.mp4?t=1749902158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏功能:</h2><strong>沉浸式故事:</strong> <br>关于亚伦努力恢复记忆和现实的神秘故事。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049150/extras/784b3c5bf799845fb16d450d2e271d18.poster.avif?t=1749902158\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049150/extras/784b3c5bf799845fb16d450d2e271d18.webm?t=1749902158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049150/extras/784b3c5bf799845fb16d450d2e271d18.mp4?t=1749902158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>艰难抉择:</strong><br>您在整个游戏中做出的选择将决定亚伦的命运和游戏的结局。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049150/extras/2edde740d57982b905b8f723330dbd3a.poster.avif?t=1749902158\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049150/extras/2edde740d57982b905b8f723330dbd3a.webm?t=1749902158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049150/extras/2edde740d57982b905b8f723330dbd3a.mp4?t=1749902158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>心理紧张:</strong><br>令人毛骨悚然的幻觉和黑暗的氛围将带给您超现实的游戏体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049150/extras/30ddaec025c8a952d54a231d6fb45a61.poster.avif?t=1749902158\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049150/extras/30ddaec025c8a952d54a231d6fb45a61.webm?t=1749902158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049150/extras/30ddaec025c8a952d54a231d6fb45a61.mp4?t=1749902158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>冒险与神秘:</strong><br>在现实和妄想之间徘徊，亚伦将探索神秘世界时遇到许多奇怪的事物并遭遇危险。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049150/extras/dc98dc4909def6c37321b2c8e0473d60.poster.avif?t=1749902158\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049150/extras/dc98dc4909def6c37321b2c8e0473d60.webm?t=1749902158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049150/extras/dc98dc4909def6c37321b2c8e0473d60.mp4?t=1749902158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>惊喜结局:</strong><br>没有人知道游戏结束时亚伦会遇到什么。您做出的决定会影响最终结果。<br><br>",
